data.description: Spacious 3 BR, 2/A waterfront home in Hampton Lakes gated 55+ community. This home is equipped with accordion hurricane shutters throughout, 2-car garage, spacious rooms with large  eat-in kitchen, screened patio overlooking lake in addition to an adjacent open patio.  A bonus is an enclosed lanai directly off of the screened patio.  Pet friendly, low maintenance ($290/month, increasing to $300 January 1, 2024), Flooring is tiled throughout with the exception of one bedroom which is wood laminate .Large  master bedroom has walk in shower with two separate vanities.
